=head1 DESCRIPTION

Details about a training plan offering.

For more information about how to reserve GPU capacity for your
SageMaker HyperPod clusters using Amazon SageMaker Training Plan, see
C< CreateTrainingPlan
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sagemaker/latest/APIReference/API_CreateTrainingPlan.html)
>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CurrencyCode => Str

The currency code for the upfront fee (e.g., USD).


=head2 DurationHours => Int

The number of whole hours in the total duration for this training plan
offering.


=head2 DurationMinutes => Int

The additional minutes beyond whole hours in the total duration for
this training plan offering.


=head2 RequestedEndTimeBefore => Str

The requested end time that the user specified when searching for the
training plan offering.


=head2 RequestedStartTimeAfter => Str

The requested start time that the user specified when searching for the
training plan offering.


=head2 ReservedCapacityOfferings => ArrayRef[L<Paws::SageMaker::ReservedCapacityOffering>]

A list of reserved capacity offerings associated with this training
plan offering.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TargetResources => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The target resources (e.g., SageMaker Training Jobs, SageMaker
HyperPod) for this training plan offering.

Training plans are specific to their target resource.

=over

=item *

A training plan designed for SageMaker training jobs can only be used
to schedule and run training jobs.

=item *

A training plan for HyperPod clusters can be used exclusively to
provide compute resources to a cluster's instance group.

=back



=head2 B<REQUIRED> TrainingPlanOfferingId => Str

The unique identifier for this training plan offering.


=head2 UpfrontFee => Str

The upfront fee for this training plan offering.



